summary: So I went from a surface pro 3 to a surface book 2. I’m glad I get to have my computer again ^^ Here’s my OC Mia Tram in what...
caption:
So I went from a surface pro 3 to a surface book 2. I’m glad I get to have my computer again ^^

Here’s my OC Mia Tram in what essentially was my outfit today (minus the shoes because I wear slippers a lot)

Since I have a new computer I’m gonna try do more digital work as well as traditional work :) So I hope I have the motivation.
